items.title: Posh Peanut 🌸 girls/toddler Georgette RARE backpack floral NWOT! Boutique expensive!
items.description:
hi there! switching over to this platform to try to keep my prices much lower and not have to pay so many fees! so that’s my niece “wearing” her new Posh Peanut Georgette backpack on Xmas day, but she hasn’t touched it since. she’s the MOST particular child I’ve ever met, and it drives me bonkers because I KNOW I have great taste! Posh peanut is NOT cheap, either! Enjoy this deal while you can! It does come with a little lunch/snack pouch as well. This would work for MANY different ages btw! It’s just the cutest thing! Brand new not in plastic, and I imagine my husband cut the tags off, as she is hyper aware of tags too. also, color is MUCH brighter in person! so so sweet. the front part actually has straps for a stuffed animal/baby doll, or it’s just
 a cute decoration! 
Still “gift ready” though! normally $65 + shipping, which makes it normally about $75!
items.label: posh peanut

user.about: Hey y’all!! Im a longtime seller on e b a y, coming here to try to speed up my sales by lowering prices! Hopefully i am able to create a nice customer base, and show everyone how much I take each order seriously, whether $1 or $100! As far as me, i’m pretty darn boring! I live to binge watch shows, amateur photography, love movies, traveling, and i have a MAJOR shopping addiction— for my niece and nephew! They end up not wearing half the stuff i buy, so i feel like this is a great place to give people deals so i can make room for more! (I am also addicted to Anthropologie, hence the name, so i’ll be adding Anthro too!!) please don’t hesitate to message me about a bundle deal, or local pickup is always fine too!! Fun fact: the boat in my profile pic is Cameron Diaz’s bayfront property—well, she bought it for her mom! They named the boat, “Fancy.” I learned about this from a sunset cruise. 🤩
